text.tspan: A Copious Systems website.
POP SONG NOW
Singing new songs to wonderful singers is a gift.
Pop Song Now
Addresses the moment of creation of a song.
Everyone with a song in his or her heart should know
Whatever their soul brings into the world is something
That is a part of them and is their own gift they bring
To the world.
The relation of the song creator to the world
Is a relation that does not belong to others who might sing it
Produce it or put their name on it in any other way.
POP SONG COMMUNITY
Pop Song Now
The motivation of this site comes from having sung to wonderful
singers in the first place. They are the ones who brought songs to
the world to be loved by everyone.
Pop Song Now aims to bring new creations to the voices that will
bring them to hearts and souls of the world.
The gift of the song should also benefit those who sing it. Perhaps
the unkown may become known. And, everyone will be tied to their
passion when they polish each new diamond in the rough.
